Simple class, that listens on standard input and notifies delegate about voice level.

Supports VoiceProcessing, so that possible output from iOS device is not considered in level value.

How to use:

* instance VoiceLevelNotifier class
* implement VoiceLevelNotifier delegate
* call startMonitoring on VoiceLevelNotifier delegate
* call stopMonitoring, when done

How to integrate with project:

pod 'VoiceLevelMeter', :git => "https://github.com/sarsonj/VoiceLevelMeter.git"
